&lt;p data-start=&quot;1472&quot; data-end=&quot;1520&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1472&quot; data-end=&quot;1520&quot;&gt;Account Executive – Knight Division Tactical&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1522&quot; data-end=&quot;1955&quot;&gt;KDT is expanding aggressively, and we are looking for elite-level Account Executives who thrive in competitive environments. This role is built for closers, individuals who can identify opportunities, create relationships, break into new markets, and win major contracts in the private security and defense sector. You will be on the front line of KDT’s growth, driving revenue and positioning the company for large-scale expansion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1957&quot; data-end=&quot;2181&quot;&gt;You must be disciplined, relentless, clear-thinking, and trustworthy. If you are the kind of person who sees opportunity everywhere and refuses to settle for average performance, this is the environment where you will excel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;382&quot; data-end=&quot;397&quot;&gt;AI Developer&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;399&quot; data-end=&quot;422&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;424&quot; data-end=&quot;782&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical (KDT) is seeking a technically strong and execution-driven &lt;strong data-start=&quot;508&quot; data-end=&quot;524&quot;&gt;AI Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to design, build, and deploy applied artificial intelligence solutions that support operations, intelligence, logistics, training, and internal decision-making. This role focuses on &lt;strong data-start=&quot;707&quot; data-end=&quot;731&quot;&gt;practical AI systems&lt;/strong&gt;, not academic research or experimental prototypes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;784&quot; data-end=&quot;974&quot;&gt;The AI Developer works closely with operations, intelligence, logistics, and engineering stakeholders to turn real operational needs into reliable, secure, and maintainable AI-enabled tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;418&quot; data-end=&quot;441&quot;&gt;Blockchain Developer&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;443&quot; data-end=&quot;466&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;468&quot; data-end=&quot;868&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a technically capable and execution-focused &lt;strong data-start=&quot;554&quot; data-end=&quot;578&quot;&gt;Blockchain Developer&lt;/strong&gt; to design, build, and maintain distributed-ledger solutions that support secure data handling, integrity verification, automation, and mission-critical workflows. This role focuses on &lt;strong data-start=&quot;763&quot; data-end=&quot;803&quot;&gt;practical blockchain implementations&lt;/strong&gt;, not speculative token projects or promotional Web3 initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;870&quot; data-end=&quot;1079&quot;&gt;The Blockchain Developer will work closely with engineering, operations, intelligence, and leadership teams to translate real organizational needs into secure, auditable, and reliable blockchain-based systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;304&quot; data-end=&quot;334&quot;&gt;Communications Element&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;336&quot; data-end=&quot;359&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;361&quot; data-end=&quot;803&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking reliable and technically competent &lt;strong data-start=&quot;438&quot; data-end=&quot;470&quot;&gt;Telecommunications Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to support domestic and international missions through the setup, operation, and maintenance of mission-critical communications systems. This role is essential to operational success and requires individuals capable of establishing and maintaining secure, reliable communications in dynamic, austere, and high-pressure environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;805&quot; data-end=&quot;1000&quot;&gt;Telecommunications Operators are responsible for enabling command, control, and coordination by ensuring continuous communications between operational elements before, during, and after missions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4683&quot; data-end=&quot;4706&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;4687&quot; data-end=&quot;4706&quot;&gt;Job Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4708&quot; data-end=&quot;5052&quot;&gt;The Construction &amp;amp; Infrastructure Operator supports the building, reinforcement, and maintenance of defense-related facilities, including bases, field installations, manufacturing structures, and specialized infrastructure. Work includes hands-on construction, heavy equipment operation, and adherence to strict military-grade safety practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;5054&quot; data-end=&quot;5080&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;5058&quot; data-end=&quot;5078&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;5081&quot; data-end=&quot;5611&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5081&quot; data-end=&quot;5172&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5083&quot; data-end=&quot;5172&quot;&gt;Execute construction, installation, and repair tasks on defense infrastructure projects&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5173&quot; data-end=&quot;5268&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5175&quot; data-end=&quot;5268&quot;&gt;Operate heavy equipment (earthmovers, lifts, generators, etc.) in a safe, controlled manner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5269&quot; data-end=&quot;5331&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5271&quot; data-end=&quot;5331&quot;&gt;Work with blueprints, site layouts, and construction plans&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5332&quot; data-end=&quot;5402&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5334&quot; data-end=&quot;5402&quot;&gt;Perform routine inspections and assist with structural maintenance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5403&quot; data-end=&quot;5469&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5405&quot; data-end=&quot;5469&quot;&gt;Ensure compliance with OSHA and defense construction protocols&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5470&quot; data-end=&quot;5539&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5472&quot; data-end=&quot;5539&quot;&gt;Coordinate with engineering teams to execute project requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;5540&quot; data-end=&quot;5611&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;5542&quot; data-end=&quot;5611&quot;&gt;Maintain site cleanliness, safety controls, and equipment readiness&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;347&quot; data-end=&quot;364&quot;&gt;Drone Operator&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;366&quot; data-end=&quot;389&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;391&quot; data-end=&quot;836&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking disciplined and technically proficient &lt;strong data-start=&quot;472&quot; data-end=&quot;491&quot;&gt;Drone Operators&lt;/strong&gt; to support domestic and international operations across security, intelligence, reconnaissance, and mission support environments. This role requires strong unmanned aerial systems (UAS) operating skills, strict adherence to aviation and operational regulations, and the ability to support mission teams in dynamic and time-sensitive conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;838&quot; data-end=&quot;1065&quot;&gt;Drone Operators are expected to function as integral members of mission teams, providing real-time aerial intelligence, situational awareness, and operational support in accordance with mission objectives and command direction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3743&quot; data-end=&quot;3766&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3747&quot; data-end=&quot;3766&quot;&gt;Job Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3768&quot; data-end=&quot;4048&quot;&gt;The Engineering Specialist supports the design, optimization, testing, and lifecycle management of defense-sector systems, equipment, and infrastructure. This role works closely with senior engineers and project managers to execute engineering tasks with precision and compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;4050&quot; data-end=&quot;4076&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;4054&quot; data-end=&quot;4074&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;4077&quot; data-end=&quot;4596&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4077&quot; data-end=&quot;4147&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4079&quot; data-end=&quot;4147&quot;&gt;Assist in developing technical designs, schematics, and prototypes&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4148&quot; data-end=&quot;4223&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4150&quot; data-end=&quot;4223&quot;&gt;Conduct field tests, performance evaluations, and equipment diagnostics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4224&quot; data-end=&quot;4295&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4226&quot; data-end=&quot;4295&quot;&gt;Review technical documents, specifications, and safety requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4296&quot; data-end=&quot;4376&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4298&quot; data-end=&quot;4376&quot;&gt;Coordinate with manufacturing and construction teams for project integration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4377&quot; data-end=&quot;4447&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4379&quot; data-end=&quot;4447&quot;&gt;Support failure analysis, troubleshooting, and system optimization&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4448&quot; data-end=&quot;4521&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4450&quot; data-end=&quot;4521&quot;&gt;Maintain documentation required for compliance with defense standards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;4522&quot; data-end=&quot;4596&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;4524&quot; data-end=&quot;4596&quot;&gt;Ensure engineering projects meet performance, cost, and timeline goals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Hacker&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a disciplined and technically capable &lt;strong&gt;Hacker&lt;/strong&gt; to support offensive and defensive cybersecurity operations. This role focuses on penetration testing, vulnerability assessment, network exploitation, and security research to protect KDT&#39;s systems and support mission-critical cyber operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Hacker works closely with operations, intelligence, and technical teams to identify vulnerabilities, simulate adversary tactics, and strengthen KDT&#39;s overall security posture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct penetration testing and red team assessments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and exploit vulnerabilities in networks, systems, and applications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform security research and threat analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain offensive security tools and techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document findings and provide remediation recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support incident response and threat hunting operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of network protocols, operating systems, and security concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with penetration testing tools (Burp Suite, Metasploit, Nmap, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of web application security (OWASP Top 10)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work under pressure in high-stakes environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;343&quot; data-end=&quot;398&quot;&gt;Intelligence Unit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;400&quot; data-end=&quot;423&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;425&quot; data-end=&quot;796&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a disciplined and detail-oriented &lt;strong data-start=&quot;501&quot; data-end=&quot;525&quot;&gt;Intelligence&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to support domestic and international security operations through timely, accurate, and actionable intelligence. This role focuses on threat analysis, risk assessment, and operational intelligence support for protective, crisis-response, and mission-driven environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;798&quot; data-end=&quot;1011&quot;&gt;The Intelligence Analyst will work closely with operations, aviation, medical, and leadership elements to support planning, decision-making, and risk mitigation across dynamic and often high-consequence scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;369&quot; data-end=&quot;404&quot;&gt;Pilot (Fixed-Wing &amp;amp; Rotary-Wing)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;406&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;430&quot; data-end=&quot;880&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking highly disciplined and mission-oriented &lt;strong data-start=&quot;512&quot; data-end=&quot;549&quot;&gt;Fixed-Wing and Rotary-Wing Pilots&lt;/strong&gt; to support domestic and international operations across security, crisis response, logistics, and specialized missions. This role requires exceptional aeronautical skill, sound judgment under pressure, and the ability to operate in complex, high-risk environments while adhering to strict safety, legal, and operational standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;Pilots will operate as part of integrated teams supporting KDT missions, with responsibilities extending beyond flight operations to include mission planning, coordination, and post-mission reporting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;127&quot; data-end=&quot;176&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;129&quot; data-end=&quot;176&quot;&gt;Knight (Private Military Contractor) – Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;178&quot; data-end=&quot;775&quot;&gt;KDT Agents provide professional security and mission-support services in domestic and international environments. The role includes protective work, site security, reconnaissance tasks, crisis response support, and operations in demanding or austere conditions. Candidates must demonstrate discipline, physical readiness, sound judgment, and the ability to work effectively as part of a small, coordinated team. Prior military or security experience, especially in combat arms, special operations, reconnaissance, communications, or deployments to Africa, Latin America or the Middle East, is strongly preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;200&quot; data-end=&quot;220&quot;&gt;Legal Associate&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;281&quot; data-end=&quot;609&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a reliable and detail-oriented Legal Associate to support the company’s legal and regulatory functions. This role supports both domestic and international operations and plays a key role in ensuring contractual, corporate, and regulatory compliance across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;611&quot; data-end=&quot;637&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;1151&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;730&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;640&quot; data-end=&quot;730&quot;&gt;Assist with drafting, reviewing, and organizing contracts, NDAs, and legal documentation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;731&quot; data-end=&quot;856&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;733&quot; data-end=&quot;856&quot;&gt;Support compliance efforts related to U.S. and international regulations with the compliance team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;857&quot; data-end=&quot;928&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;859&quot; data-end=&quot;928&quot;&gt;Conduct legal research and prepare internal summaries and memoranda&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;929&quot; data-end=&quot;993&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;931&quot; data-end=&quot;993&quot;&gt;Maintain organized, audit-ready legal records&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;994&quot; data-end=&quot;1104&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;996&quot; data-end=&quot;1104&quot;&gt;Support risk identification and policy implementation in coordination with leadership and operations teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1105&quot; data-end=&quot;1151&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1107&quot; data-end=&quot;1151&quot;&gt;Coordinate with external counsel as needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1153&quot; data-end=&quot;1173&quot;&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1174&quot; data-end=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1174&quot; data-end=&quot;1242&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1176&quot; data-end=&quot;1242&quot;&gt;Background in Law, Legal Studies or a related field&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1243&quot; data-end=&quot;1298&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1245&quot; data-end=&quot;1298&quot;&gt;Strong research, writing, and organizational skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1299&quot; data-end=&quot;1366&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1301&quot; data-end=&quot;1366&quot;&gt;High attention to detail, discretion, and professional judgment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1367&quot; data-end=&quot;1433&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1369&quot; data-end=&quot;1433&quot;&gt;Ability to manage sensitive information and work independently&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1434&quot; data-end=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1436&quot; data-end=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;Professional proficiency in English (Spanish is a plus)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1493&quot; data-end=&quot;1508&quot;&gt;Preferred&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1509&quot; data-end=&quot;1668&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1509&quot; data-end=&quot;1598&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1511&quot; data-end=&quot;1598&quot;&gt;Exposure to regulated industries such as security, defense, or government contracting&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;862&quot; data-end=&quot;883&quot;&gt;Logistics Operator&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;885&quot; data-end=&quot;908&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;910&quot; data-end=&quot;1321&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking dependable and execution-focused&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;985&quot; data-end=&quot;1008&quot;&gt;Logistics Operators&lt;/strong&gt; to support domestic and international missions through hands-on logistical execution and sustainment. This role is mission-critical and requires individuals who can operate under pressure, manage equipment and movement in dynamic environments, and support operational teams before, during, and after deployments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1323&quot; data-end=&quot;1492&quot;&gt;Logistics Operators are responsible for ensuring personnel, equipment, and resources are available, functional, and properly accounted for in support of live operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;2679&quot; data-end=&quot;2702&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2683&quot; data-end=&quot;2702&quot;&gt;Job Information&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2704&quot; data-end=&quot;3059&quot;&gt;The Manufacturing Technician supports the production of mission-critical defense components, systems, and equipment used across military and strategic programs. This role is responsible for operating industrial machinery, assembling components, conducting quality inspections, and maintaining production discipline to meet strict defense-sector standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;3061&quot; data-end=&quot;3087&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;3065&quot; data-end=&quot;3085&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;3088&quot; data-end=&quot;3672&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3088&quot; data-end=&quot;3168&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3090&quot; data-end=&quot;3168&quot;&gt;Operate manufacturing machinery, tools, and equipment safely and effectively&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3169&quot; data-end=&quot;3252&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3171&quot; data-end=&quot;3252&quot;&gt;Assemble mechanical/electrical components according to technical specifications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3253&quot; data-end=&quot;3341&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3255&quot; data-end=&quot;3341&quot;&gt;Perform quality checks and maintain compliance with ISO, DoD, and internal standards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3342&quot; data-end=&quot;3426&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3344&quot; data-end=&quot;3426&quot;&gt;Maintain accurate production logs, inventory records, and workflow documentation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3427&quot; data-end=&quot;3508&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3429&quot; data-end=&quot;3508&quot;&gt;Identify production issues and coordinate corrective actions with supervisors&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3509&quot; data-end=&quot;3581&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3511&quot; data-end=&quot;3581&quot;&gt;Support preventive maintenance tasks and shop-floor safety protocols&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;3582&quot; data-end=&quot;3672&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;3584&quot; data-end=&quot;3672&quot;&gt;Work collaboratively with engineering and logistics teams to meet production deadlines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;371&quot; data-end=&quot;396&quot;&gt;Medical Element&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;398&quot; data-end=&quot;421&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;422&quot; data-end=&quot;839&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking highly capable &lt;strong data-start=&quot;479&quot; data-end=&quot;507&quot;&gt;Tactical Medics&lt;/strong&gt; to support domestic and international operations across security, crisis response, disaster relief, and high-risk environments. This role requires advanced pre-hospital medical skills, disciplined decision-making under pressure, and the ability to operate effectively alongside security and aviation elements in austere conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;841&quot; data-end=&quot;1048&quot;&gt;Medics are expected to function as integral members of mission teams, providing immediate life-saving care, advising leadership on medical risk, and supporting operational continuity in dynamic environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;882&quot; data-end=&quot;1082&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;391&quot; data-end=&quot;404&quot;&gt;Programmer&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;406&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;431&quot; data-end=&quot;824&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a disciplined and technically capable &lt;strong data-start=&quot;511&quot; data-end=&quot;525&quot;&gt;Programmer&lt;/strong&gt; to support internal systems, operational tools, and mission-critical software needs. This role focuses on building, maintaining, and improving software solutions that support planning, coordination, data handling, training, and operational efficiency across KDT’s security and operations ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;826&quot; data-end=&quot;1024&quot;&gt;The Programmer works closely with operations, intelligence, logistics, and leadership elements to translate real operational requirements into reliable, secure, and maintainable technical solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;343&quot; data-end=&quot;398&quot;&gt;Propaganda Unit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;400&quot; data-end=&quot;423&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;415&quot; data-end=&quot;436&quot;&gt;Position Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;438&quot; data-end=&quot;891&quot;&gt;Knight Division Tactical is seeking a disciplined, analytically minded &lt;strong data-start=&quot;509&quot; data-end=&quot;563&quot;&gt;Propagandist&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to support domestic and international operations through &lt;strong data-start=&quot;621&quot; data-end=&quot;709&quot;&gt;deliberate narrative development, digital influence, and controlled public messaging&lt;/strong&gt;. This role focuses on shaping perception, building trust, and supporting recruitment and strategic positioning across high-risk, mission-driven environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;893&quot; data-end=&quot;1289&quot;&gt;The Propagandist will be responsible for designing and executing &lt;strong data-start=&quot;958&quot; data-end=&quot;1004&quot;&gt;platform-specific communication strategies&lt;/strong&gt; across social media, digital channels, and public-facing content while operating within strict operational, legal, and reputational constraints. The role requires a deep understanding of online platforms, audience targeting, performance analytics, and risk-aware content distribution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1291&quot; data-end=&quot;1661&quot;&gt;The Propagandist will work closely with &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1331&quot; data-end=&quot;1396&quot;&gt;leadership, operations, intelligence, and recruiting elements&lt;/strong&gt; to ensure messaging aligns with operational realities, security considerations, and long-term strategic objectives. This position demands judgment, discretion, and the ability to operate effectively in environments where miscommunication carries real consequences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
